<font size="4">Hi all:<br><br></font><pre><font><font><font><font size="4">I&#39;m using openmpi-1.4.2</font></font></font></font>. <font><font size="4">I need to run pvserver(a mpi program of paraview) in a cluster. I have Mac OS X 10.6.4 in all my hosts and in the server. I had configure ssh<br>
